<tr>
  <td class="diff-marker">&#160;</td>
  <td class="diff-context"><div>Isolation increases the feelings of loneliness and depression, fear of other people, or even create a more negative self-image. There is a realization in the individual that their isolating is not 'normal behavior' and can create the feeling that there is a whole world going on that they are not or unable to be a part of. A feeling of being detached can create at times an inner panic.</div></td>
  <td class="diff-marker">&#160;</td>
  <td class="diff-context"><div>Isolation increases the feelings of loneliness and depression, fear of other people, or even create a more negative self-image. There is a realization in the individual that their isolating is not 'normal behavior' and can create the feeling that there is a whole world going on that they are not or unable to be a part of. A feeling of being detached can create at times an inner panic.</div></td>
</tr>
